{% set name = "spatialgeometry" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}

    - cross-python_{{ target_platform }}     # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - numpy                                  # [build_platform != target_platform]

    - numpy
    - pip
    - python
  run:

    - spatialmath-python >=1.0.0
    - numpy

    - spatialgeometry
    - spatialgeometry.tools
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

  license_file: LICENSE
